?</h2>\r\nWe endeavor to monitor all the content that appears on this site. If you believe you have found objectionable content, please email nyashimmerwall@wcs.org.\r\n<h2>MY PROBLEM IS NOT LISTED IN THE FAQ. WHO CAN I CONTACT FOR HELP?</h2>\r\nPlease contact nyashimmerwall@wcs.org and be assured you will receive a prompt response.','Other questions','','publish','closed','closed','','faq-other-questions','','','2014-05-11 18:12:18','2014-05-11 18:12:18','',0,'http://ny3.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=257',0,'faq','',0),(258,1,'2014-05-11 18:09:08','2014-05-11 18:09:08','<a href=\"back\" id=\"back-to-main\">Back</a>\r\n[faq]','FAQ','','inherit','open','open','','58-revision-v1','','','2014-05-11 18:09:08','2014-05-11 18:09:08','',58,'http://ny3.dev/58-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(259,1,'2014-05-11 18:29:19','2014-05-11 18:29:19','<a href=\"/\" id=\"back-to-main\">Back</a>\r\n[faq]','FAQ','','inherit','open','open','','58-revision-v1','','','2014-05-11 18:29:19','2014-05-11 18:29:19','',58,'http://ny3.dev/58-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(260,1,'2014-05-12 16:53:30','2014-05-12 16:53:30','<div id=\"donation-container\"><div id=\"donation-header\">\r\n \r\n        <form id=\"cnvDonationForm-form\" action=\"\" method=\"post\">\r\n        \r\n        <h1>Choose donation amount</h1>\r\n        <h2>Together we can create Ocean Wonders: Sharks! and build a new New York Aquarium for generations of curious minds to come.</h2>\r\n        </div><div id=\"donation-body\"><div id=\"step-1\"><div class=\"selection\">\r\n                <a href=\"donate-oval\" class=\"oval donate-oval\">25</a>\r\n                <div class=\"donation-content twenty-five\">\r\n                        <div class=\"donation-amount\">$25</div>\r\n                        <div class=\"donation-reference\">Friend</div>\r\n                        <div class=\"donation-info\">you will receive a personalized tile on the virtual shimmer wall</div>\r\n                </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n          